lead_paragraph: Tomas Berdych's chances of qualifying for the ATP Finals were dealt a blow Monday as Nikoloz Basilashvili of Georgia defeated the 10th-ranked Czech 6-4, 6-7 (5), 7-5 in the first round of the Erste Bank Open.

headline.print_headline: Basilashvili Upsets 2nd-Seeded Berdych in 3 Sets in Vienna
headline.main: Basilashvili Upsets 2nd-Seeded Berdych in 3 Sets in Vienna
